        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_mamba.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 914f0c3c-f4a7-46e5-a672-0792f8f30fd4).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47. Your client, Salvatore Bravuomo wants to humiliate Marco Abiatti to lower his chances of winning. You will need to take out his 4 most trusted employees. Mulo, his eye in the sky tells him what to say and what to do. Donati is his ground worker. He announces Abiatti and hypes him up on stage. Attento is the lead tech officer and treasurer for his campaign. Vassallo is a oil tycoon leader and pledged millions of dollars to Abbiati&apos;s campaign. Good luck 47.",
